cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM 

This paper deals with the task of visual question answering and visual grounding, which involves combining textual and visual information. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper proposes a new pooling method, which involves combining features from different modalities, making it relevant to the Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with multimodal data, which is relevant to the Multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
